name: White VYBZ Skater
description:
White VYBZ Skater

Joseph La-placa was born in sunny slough during 1991 & recently graduated from the arts university bournemouth with a BA hons in illustration.

Constantly cold He creates works about the twisted truth & everyday life he portrays this in a cauldron of dark morbid creatures, animals, nature and black hearted humor. The relationship in line and mark making play’s an important part in his practice creating certain moods and depth’s.

Joseph spends most his time day dreaming in a haze of a more wonderful place.

All Our Tee's are 100% cotton and are printed and hand crafted in the UK using the best printing techniques available. 

All payments are safe and secure and are all guaranteed by PayPal. We ship our Tee's using First Class Royal Mail and if ordered before 1pm they tend to arrive the next day. 
 
Any questions or queries feel free to get in contact and we will get right back to you. 


Size Guide- Chest 

S - 34/36"
M - 38/40"
L - 42/44"   
XL - 46/48"
